POST /v1/message
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
Body: { "text": "...", "lang": "hi", "session_id": "..." }

POST /v1/voice
Body: multipart/form-data audio file, metadata

POST /v1/verify/aadhaar
Body: { "consent_id": "...", "masked_aadhaar_last4": "1234" }

GET /v1/ticket/{ticket_id}
POST /v1/ticket  -> create grievance (auto-assign dept)
